      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified-1\n\nTests uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-38vm1 for review-dne-part-1 received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/20e8a1a0-0360-11e6-9b34-5254006e85c2). Ran 9 tests.  1 tests failed: conf-sanity.",
