          "tz": 330
        },
        "subject": "LU-6488 tests: remove the check for ZFS to test large file",
        "message": "LU-6488 tests: remove the check for ZFS to test large file\n\ntest_250 calls getstripe on a file before creating it and\ncan fail test as it doesn't exists.\n\nThis patch removes the check altogether thus enabling\nthe large file test to run irrespective of FS type,\ne.g. LDISKFS or ZFS.\n\nChange-Id: Iababa48093f70cdd6eba73458a706b25bf971999\nSigned-off-by: Parinay Kondekar <parinay.kondekar@seagate.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
